Package: lisfR
Title: R Tools for Open-Source Large-Scale Hydrological Models and Satellite Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Manh-Hung", "Le", email = "manhhung.le510@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of R utilities for reading, writing, and processing
    NetCDF outputs from land surface models such as LIS and FLDAS, along with
    satellite-derived datasets including CHIRPS, MODIS, and SWOT. Provides
    tools to convert NetCDF files into georeferenced raster stacks, export
    rasters back to NetCDF, calculate model domain boundaries from shapefiles,
    and compare model outputs across ensembles and time.
